  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package re-evaluates COU1 at Model Risk Level 3 following an expanded regulatory submission scope. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are fully assessed and meet or exceed required levels. The 'Equivalency of input parameters' factor is recorded as not-assessed on the basis that the assessment team judged it inapplicable to a purely computational sensitivity study with no physical test article — however the factor encoding reflects not-assessed rather than not-applicable, and no formal scoping justification was documented.",
