      "rationale": "FDA pump experimental data obtained at 2500 RPM, 2.5 L/min and 5.0 L/min. Boundary conditions in simulation match experimental inlet flow rates and outlet pressure within 3%. Temperature and fluid properties (bovine blood, 37°C) documented and consistent. Required level 2 achieved."
