      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index (RH) is the primary QoI in both the validation activity and the COU decision. The power-law hemolysis damage accumulation model is applied identically in validation and COU simulations. Direct correspondence confirmed. Required level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
