      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump — the same geometry as the COU device. Operating conditions span the full COU envelope (2.5–5.0 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Reynolds number regime and turbulence characteristics consistent between validation and COU. Required level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence demonstrated to residual tolerance sufficient that solver error is negligible relative to discretization error.",
      "rationale": "All simulations converged to residual tolerance of 1×10⁻⁶ for continuity and momentum equations. Mass imbalance across domain < 0.01%. Iterative convergence error estimated at < 0.2% of QoI, negligible relative to GCI of 1.8%. Required level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
