    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-biofluid-lab-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are assessed and meet or exceed required levels for MRL 3. The 'Equivalency of input parameters' factor was informally judged inapplicable by the assessment team and recorded as not-assessed. The team concluded that the remaining assessed factors collectively provide sufficient evidence to support the COU decision, accepting the hemolysis CFD model for identification of worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The not-assessed factor was not formally scoped out and no structured applicability review was documented, but the team judged the residual credibility gap acceptable given the strong performance on all other factors.",
